Class Controller

  • java.lang.Object

      • getDataBaseNames

        public Widget getDataBaseNames​(int givenID)
        Compares the productID from production record database and product database to see if there is a match. If a match occurs then an object of Widget is created to return values of that product row to use product name in productionRecord toString.
        Parameters:
        givenID - ProductId from productionRecord.
        Returns:
        A Widget object if match is successful.
